OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy with
OL,6,Foccasional mainly light rain at first
OL,7,Fbut becoming dry through the evening
OL,8,Fwith some clear spells developing.
OL,9,FCloud increases again overnight with
OL,10,Foutbreaks of rain later. Winds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FMostly cloudy with outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain, heaviest and most persistent
OL,14,Facross western parts, the rain turning
OL,15,Fmore showery in the afternoon, with a
OL,16,Frisk of thunder. Occasionally fresh
OL,17,Fsoutherly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
