OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy,
OL,6,Fshowery overnight rain soon clearing
OL,7,Fthen sunny spells and showers Sunday.
OL,8,FMainly dry and bright Monday by cloud
OL,9,Fincreasing with evening rain, with
OL,10,Fsunny spells and showers Tuesday.
